data.description: Bright and Spacious Westport Farm Townhome with 3/2.5, Fireplace in the Family Room, Hardwood floors featured in the Foyer, Kitchen and Dining Room, Deck, Expansive Finished Basement and Garage. Convenient second floor Laundry.  Three floors of living space!  Freshly painted and brand new carpeting throughout. Located within a few miles of the Turnpike. Souderton School District. Surrounding areas include Hatfield, Lansdale, Harleysville and Telford. Available May 4, 2014 for $1850/month plus utilities and sewer. Pets OK at owners' discretion and with additional $50 monthly pet fee. Please call Janine at 267-218-0411.
